'''''Dungeon Master''''' is a [[role-playing video game]] featuring a [[2.5D|pseudo-3D]] [[First-person (video games)|first-person perspective]]. It was developed and published by [[FTL Games]] for the [[Atari ST]] in 1987,<ref name=gamasutra>{{cite web
