 |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/features/20070223b/barton_06.shtml 
 |publisher=[[Gamasutra]] 
 |access-date=2009-03-26 
 |url-status=dead 
 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090330222054/http://www.gamasutra.com/features/20070223b/barton_06.shtml 
 |archive-date=2009-03-30 
}}</ref> almost identical [[Amiga]] and [[MS-DOS|PC (DOS)]] ports following in 1988 and 1992.

''Dungeon Master'' sold 40,000 copies in its year of release alone,<ref name="Dragon #200">{{cite magazine
