ch 2016 | pages=64–80}}</ref> In 1996, GamesMaster listed the game 42nd in their Top 100 Games of All Time.<ref>{{Cite journal |date=July 1996 |title=Top 100 Games of All Time |url=https://retrocdn.net/images/c/cf/GamesMaster_UK_044.pdf |journal=GamesMaster |issue=44 |pages=76}}</ref>

